 The egg craked. A green fog exited it in a rush. Tne fog emitted from the 
open hole leading to the surface. Bursting out of it would be what would look 
like a 3 foot lizard. It's eyes blood red , his tounge hissing. He knew ehere 
he was now. It would only be a matter of time until he gained his first 
stage. He was completly vulnerable in this stage. He need the dna smaples to 
evolve. He sent a burts of masquito bots out of his tail. The scattered up 
and out of the hole. He knew he could not yet leave for he was far to 
vulnerable. The masquitos each had thier destened course.....
